<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 10<unclear>37</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>jula pravarddhamānavijayarājyasaṁvatsa 46 śrahi gaṁggagoṇḍacō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḍavalanāṁṭi guddavādināṁṭi peddaḍākarēmi śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvara
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ku viṣuvusaṁkrāṁtinimittamuna jayaṁgoṇḍacōḍamaṇḍalamuna <unclear>pu</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟakōṭṭattu kaṇḍraya<unclear>pē</unclear>rūrunāṭṭu kṣatriyaśikhāmaṇinallūru vellāla
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṇḍu vāmanakkiyāṁ<unclear>ḍa</unclear>ṁgōvanu gaṁggagoṇḍacōḍavalanāṁṭi baṁṭani mā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>viṇṭivāḍa mā raṭṭaḍikamu valayucu<unclear>ṭṭa</unclear> Alamu Ēnuvuṭlu nēla gaṇṭā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>śēṣasalvisaṁpadalatōṁ gūḍaṁ Āḍavalladēvara naṁbrāṭiki
<lb n="9"/>maṁtrabōnamunappaṭiki ṟēpaṭi saṁdyakuṁ dellaṁbrāla kuṁcca
<lb n="10" break="no"/>mulu Enmidi pappu kuṁcceṇḍu neyi paṟiyaṇḍunu naṁjuḍlu 3 ṇṭiki
<lb n="11" break="no"/>gāṁ śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvarasannidhānamuna nicci śilaśāsanamu
<lb n="12"/>veṭṭiṁciti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> likhīta<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> ḍakarēmisuracāri Ayina rajēṁdracōḍa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>Ācāryyasya <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

